      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just \"financial difficulty\" though. i have people's livelihoods on my hands. i ruined everything i built. when i think about going back home and seeing the look on my dad's face, it feels like my chest is physically collapsing. there just isn't any version of the future where i'm not a walking disaster. i feel like i've already ceased to exist, i'm just waiting for the world to catch up.",
